title: #524 - Greg Fitzsimmons
description:
Greg Fitzsimmons, Comedian and Host of the "Fitzdog Radio" podcast and "The Greg Fitzsimmons Show" on SiriusXM, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio.

This podcast is brought to you by:

Lyft - Sign up to drive at Lyft.com/joey and find out how you qualify to get a $500 new driver bonus. 
 
Blue Apron: Go to blueapron.com/JOEY to get $30 off of your first meal and free shipping!
